<h1>Michael Chan (saint)</h1>
<div class="wiki-subtitle">陳紀正 · Chan Kei Ching · Born 8 December 2002, Hong Kong · Living saint · Durham University · White Tiger</div>

<div class="notice">
  ℹ️ This article is about the living saint, Theoretical Physicist, and Durham University basketball captain. For his rival, see <a href="#">Daniel Chan (dickhead)</a>.
</div>

<div class="wiki-body">
  <div class="wiki-main">

    <div class="toc">
